mobiheader.fullname: God in a Brothel: An Undercover Journey into Sex Trafficking and Rescue

exthheader.author: Walker, Daniel
exthheader.description: Undercover investigator Daniel Walker recounts how he infiltrated the multi-billion-dollar global sex industry in order to liberate women and children from slavery. In vivid firsthand accounts, Walker traces his steps through a diffuse criminal underground stretching from Southeast Asia to Las Vegas, Nevada.
